{"ID":"20260424101903-ax89zkp","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-ax89zkp","title":"90_术语表","type":"doc","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101903-1xhnbxd","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-1xhnbxd","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"90 术语表"}]},{"ID":"20260424101903-fhvo089","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-fhvo089","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"术语表只收录跨章节反复出现、且容易被混用的词。定义优先服务于快速判断，不追求辞典式铺陈。"}]},{"ID":"20260424101903-rqbulty","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-rqbulty","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当前术语"}]},{"ID":"20260424101903-0huqa8q","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-0huqa8q","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101903-sm0es6f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-sm0es6f","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101903-qw63a2y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-qw63a2y","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"NPU"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​：面向神经网络负载的专用加速器，目标通常是以更高能效执行矩阵乘加、卷积、注意力等算子。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101903-brdqdw5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-brdqdw5","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101903-rtzy2gq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101903-rtzy2gq","updated":"20260424101903"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"PE"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​：Processing Element，阵列里的最小计算单元，通常包含乘加、寄存器和局部控制。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101903-qguuyea","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Bullet